Use the message tool to send a message to a chat (DM or group). If no chat_id is provided, the message is sent to the current conversation. Use users_search to find a user's chat ID for DMs, or groups_search to find a group's chat ID. Confirm with the current user before sending -- describe who you're sending to and what the message will say. Only send after explicit confirmation. When the recipient is a different user, prefix the message content with "From <current user name>: " so the recipient knows who sent it.